<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Jerelyn Arangca | Portfolio</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    :root {
      --pink: #ec95c7;
      --purple: #b79af7;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --text: #4b3f57;
    }

    .navbar {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(183, 154, 247, 0.3);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(128, 92, 160, 0.15);
      z-index: 1000;
      padding: 15px 0;
    }

    .nav-container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      list-style: none;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: var(--purple);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      background: var(--purple);
      color: white;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fde7f4, #f4e9ff);
      color: var(--text);
      padding-top: 160px; /* INCREASED - now properly separated */
      padding-left: 16px;
      padding-right: 16px;
      padding-bottom: 50px;
    }

    .page {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 30px; /* Increased gap between sections */
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      border: 1px solid rgba(183, 154, 247, 0.2);
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(128, 92, 160, 0.12);
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 0.7fr;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .small-label {
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--pink);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.6rem);
      color: var(--purple);
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .hero h2 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--pink);
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .intro {
      margin-top: 14px;
      max-width: 520px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .hero-photo {
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-photo img {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 5px solid var(--white);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(183, 154, 247, 0.18);
    }

    .about h3, .details h3, .skills h3, .inspiration h3 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: var(--purple);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .about p, .inspiration p {
      line-height: 1.9;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .details-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .details-list div {
      background: #fff8fd;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 4px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(236, 149, 199, 0.18);
    }

    .details-list span {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #7a6b88;
    }

    .details-list strong {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .skill-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .skill-item {
      background: #fff8fd;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 16px;
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid rgba(183, 154, 247, 0.18);
    }

    .skill-item span {
      display: block;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--purple);
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .skill-item small {
      color: var(--pink);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .inspiration {
      text-align: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .hero, .grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .hero { text-align: center; }
      .intro { margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
      .hero-photo img { width: 180px; height: 180px; }
      body { padding-top: 140px; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 520px) {
      body { padding-top: 130px; }
      .card { padding: 20px; }
      .skill-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-photo img { width: 160px; height: 160px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="nav-container">
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="#about">About Me</a></li>
        <li><a href="#details">Personal Details</a></li>
        <li><a href="#skills">Skills / Programming Languages</a></li>
        <li><a href="#inspiration">Inspiration as a Programmer</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="page">
    <section class="hero card">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <p class="small-label">PORTFOLIO</p>
        <h1>Jerelyn Arangca Daileg</h1>
        <h2>Aspiring Web Designer</h2>
        <p class="intro">A motivated student who is passionate about technology, creativity, and building simple digital solutions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-photo">
        <img src="cuteako1.jpg" alt="Jerelyn Arangca Daileg">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card about" id="about">
      <h3>About Me</h3>
      <p>I am <strong>Jerelyn Arangca Daileg</strong>, <strong>18 years old</strong> a <strong>BSIT 1-B</strong> student at <strong>Our Lady of the Sacred Heart College of Guimba</strong>. I am interested in technology, web design, and programming because I enjoy creating useful and simple digital projects. My goal is to keep learning and improve my skills.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="grid">
      <section class="card details" id="details">
        <h3>Personal Details</h3>
        <div class="details-list">
          <div><span>Full Name</span><strong>Jerelyn Arangca Daileg</strong></div>
          <div><span>Age</span><strong>18</strong></div>
          <div><span>Email Address</span><strong>jerelynarangcadaileg06@email.com</strong></div>
          <div><span>Address</span><strong>Manggang Marikit Guimba, Nueva Ecija</strong></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="card skills" id="skills">
        <h3>Skills / Programming Languages</h3>
        <div class="skill-list">
          <div class="skill-item"><span>HTML</span><small>Beginner</small></div>
          <div class="skill-item"><span>CSS</span><small>Beginner</small></div>
          <div class="skill-item"><span>JavaScript</span><small>Beginner</small></div>
          <div class="skill-item"><span>Java</span><small>Beginner</small></div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </section>

    <section class="card inspiration" id="inspiration">
      <h3>Inspiration as a Programmer</h3>
      <p>I did not choose IT just because many people say it is in demand. That is true, but it is not my main reason. I chose IT because I can see my future in this course. I believe that someday, this course can help me have a better and comfortable life. That is why I am working hard now, studying and improving my skills. I also want to learn more about technology and use it to help myself and my family in the future.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>